                  THRU 2500-BUSCA-CLI-EXIT
               IF DB2-OK
                  MOVE COCD5403-GNOME    TO WS-GNOMECLI3
               ELSE
                  MOVE SPACES            TO WS-GNOMECLI3
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ3-S
                  MOVE COCK0001-CLIENTE-N-EXISTS
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ3-MSG
                  MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ3-CAPLIC
               END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Obtem o primo n伹ero interno
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               PERFORM 2502-BUSCA-SEQ
                  THRU 2502-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT
               MOVE WS-NSEQ TO WS-NSEQ3
               IF WS-NSEQ1 NOT = ZEROS
                  ADD 1 TO WS-NSEQ3
               END-IF
               IF WS-NSEQ2 NOT = ZEROS
                  ADD 1 TO WS-NSEQ3
               END-IF
           END-IF.

       2853-VALIDA-DESPESA3-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * VALIDA DESPESA 04
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2854-VALIDA-DESPESA4.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2854-VALIDA-DESPESA4' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *-----------------------------*
      *--- Valida Quarta Despesa ---*
      *-----------------------------*
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDPROJ4 EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDDESP4 EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-CIDDESP4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-CIDDESP4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-CIDDESP4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-DTREG4   EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-DTREG4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-DTREG4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-DTREG4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-MVLR4    EQUAL ZEROS
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-MVLR4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-MVLR4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-MVLR4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CMOED4   EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-CMOED4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-CMOED4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-CMOED4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- Se Tipo de despesa 004 - Desloca鈬o em viatura prria, os
      *--- campos GTRAJECTO, NKMS e GMOTIVO s縊 obrigatios.
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDDESP4 EQUAL COCK0002-TIPDSP-VIATPRP
           AND COCV6810-GTRAJECTO4 EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-GTRAJECTO4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-GTRAJECTO4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-GTRAJECTO4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDDESP4 EQUAL COCK0002-TIPDSP-VIATPRP
           AND COCV6810-NKMS4    EQUAL ZEROS
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-NKMS4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-NKMS4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-NKMS4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDDESP4 EQUAL COCK0002-TIPDSP-VIATPRP
           AND COCV6810-GMOTIVO4 EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-GMOTIVO4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV6811-GMOTIVO4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-GMOTIVO4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- Se Tipo de despesa diferente 004 - Desloca鈬o em viatura
      *--- prria, os campos GTRAJECTO, NKMS e GMOTIVO estar縊
      *--- obrigatiamente vazios
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDDESP4   NOT EQUAL COCK0002-TIPDSP-VIATPRP
           AND COCV6810-GTRAJECTO4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-GTRAJECTO4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INVAL   TO COCV6811-GTRAJECTO4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-GTRAJECTO4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDDESP4 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-TIPDSP-VIATPRP
           AND COCV6810-NKMS4    NOT EQUAL ZEROS
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-NKMS4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INVAL   TO COCV6811-NKMS4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-NKMS4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDDESP4 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-TIPDSP-VIATPRP
           AND COCV6810-GMOTIVO4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6811-GMOTIVO4-S
              MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-INVAL   TO COCV6811-GMOTIVO4-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6811-GMOTIVO4-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- Ler Projecto
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDPROJ4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCV6810-CIDPROJ4 TO COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
               PERFORM 2800-LER-PROJECTO
                  THRU 2800-LER-PROJECTO-EXIT
               IF DB2-OK
                  MOVE COCD3605-CLIENTE  TO WS-CLIENTE4
                  MOVE COCD3605-LINHANEG TO WS-LINHANEG4
                  MOVE COCD3605-RESPONS  TO WS-RESPONS4
                  MOVE COCD3605-CPROJECT TO WS-CPROJECT4
               ELSE
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-S
                  MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-MSG
                  MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-CAPLIC
               END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Ler Respons疱el do Projecto
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDPROJ4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE WS-RESPONS4 TO COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
               PERFORM 2850-LER-RESPONS
                  THRU 2850-LER-RESPONS-EXIT
               IF DB2-OK
                  MOVE COCD5303-CUTILIZA TO WS-CUTILIZA4
               ELSE
                  MOVE SPACES            TO WS-CUTILIZA4
               END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Ler Niveis de Aprova鈬o do Projecto
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CIDPROJ4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCV6810-CIDPROJ4 TO COCD6600-NIDPROJECTO
               PERFORM 2900-LER-NIVEIS
                  THRU 2900-LER-NIVEIS-EXIT
               IF DB2-OK
                  MOVE COCD6600-CUSER01  TO WS-CUSER4-01
                  MOVE COCD6600-CUSER02  TO WS-CUSER4-02
               ELSE
                  MOVE SPACES            TO WS-CUSER4-01
                  MOVE SPACES            TO WS-CUSER4-02
               END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Ler Cliente (Designa鈬o)
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND WS-CLIENTE4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE WS-CLIENTE4 TO COCD5403-CSIGLA
               PERFORM 2500-BUSCA-CLI
                  THRU 2500-BUSCA-CLI-EXIT
               IF DB2-OK
                  MOVE COCD5403-GNOME    TO WS-GNOMECLI4
               ELSE
                  MOVE SPACES            TO WS-GNOMECLI4
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-S
                  MOVE COCK0001-CLIENTE-N-EXISTS
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-MSG
                  MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                    TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ4-CAPLIC
               END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Obtem o primo n伹ero interno
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               PERFORM 2502-BUSCA-SEQ
                  THRU 2502-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT
               MOVE WS-NSEQ TO WS-NSEQ4
               IF WS-NSEQ1 NOT = ZEROS
                  ADD 1 TO WS-NSEQ4
               END-IF
               IF WS-NSEQ2 NOT = ZEROS
                  ADD 1 TO WS-NSEQ4
               END-IF
               IF WS-NSEQ3 NOT = ZEROS
                  ADD 1 TO WS-NSEQ4
               END-IF
           END-IF.

       2854-VALIDA-DESPESA4-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * BUSCA O DESIGNAﾇﾃO DO CLIENTE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-BUSCA-CLI.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-BUSCA-CLI     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT CSIGLA, GNOME, CPAIS, CMOEDA
                 INTO  :COCD5403-CSIGLA
                     , :COCD5403-GNOME
                     , :COCD5403-CPAIS
                     , :COCD5403-CMOEDA
                 FROM COVT5403_EMPRESAS
                 WHERE CSIGLA   = :COCD5403-CSIGLA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT5403 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD5403-CMOEDA TO WS-CMOED-CLI
              ELSE
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                  TO COCV6811-CEMPRESA-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMBIO-N-EXIST
                  TO COCV6811-CEMPRESA-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                  TO COCV6811-CEMPRESA-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2500-BUSCA-CLI-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * BUSCA O DESIGNAﾇﾃO DA EMPRESA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2501-BUSCA-EMPRESA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2501-BUSCA-EMPRESA ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6810-CEMPRESA TO COCD5403-CEMPRESA.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT CSIGLA, GNOME, CPAIS, CMOEDA
                 INTO  :COCD5403-CSIGLA
                     , :COCD5403-GNOME
                     , :COCD5403-CPAIS
                     , :COCD5403-CMOEDA
                 FROM COVT5403_EMPRESAS
                 WHERE CEMPRESA = :COCD5403-CEMPRESA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT5403 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD5403-CMOEDA TO WS-CMOED-FUNC
              ELSE
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                  TO COCV6811-CEMPRESA-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CLIENTE-N-EXISTS
                  TO COCV6811-CEMPRESA-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                  TO COCV6811-CEMPRESA-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2501-BUSCA-EMPRESA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * BUSCA A SEQUENCIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2502-BUSCA-SEQ.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2502-BUSCA-SEQ     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6810-CEMPRESA TO COCD4804-CEMPRESA.
           MOVE COCV6810-CANO
             TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
           MOVE COCV6810-CMES
             TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
           MOVE CON-01
             TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO
             TO COCD4804-DTMESANO
           MOVE COCV6810-CFUNCIONARIO TO COCD4804-CIDEMP.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT IFNULL(MAX(NSEQ), 0)
                 INTO  :WS-NSEQ
                 FROM COVT4804_EXPENSE
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD4804-CIDEMP
                 AND   DTMESANO = :COCD4804-DTMESANO
                 AND   CEMPRESA = :COCD4804-CEMPRESA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT4804 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 COMPUTE WS-NSEQ = WS-NSEQ + 1
              ELSE
                 MOVE 1 TO WS-NSEQ
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2502-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * BUSCA DESCRIﾇﾃO DO PAIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2503-BUSCA-PAIS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2503-BUSCA-PAIS    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCD5403-CPAIS NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CPAIS
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCD5403-CPAIS
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO WS-GPAIS
              ELSE
                 MOVE SPACES TO WS-GPAIS
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2503-BUSCA-PAIS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * BUSCA DESCRIﾇﾃO DA LINHA DE NEGﾓCIO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2504-BUSCA-LNEG.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2504-BUSCA-LNEG    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND WS-LINHANEG NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-LNEG
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE WS-LINHANEG
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC
                   TO WS-LNEG
              ELSE
                 MOVE SPACES TO WS-LNEG
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2504-BUSCA-LNEG-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * LER PROJECTOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2800-LER-PROJECTO.

           MOVE COCK0002-NAO        TO COCD3605-ICTACUST

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT NIDPROJECTO
                      , CPROJECT
                      , CLIENTE
                      , LINHANEG
                      , RESPONS
                 INTO  :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
                    ,  :COCD3605-CPROJECT
                    ,  :COCD3605-CLIENTE
                    ,  :COCD3605-LINHANEG
                    ,  :COCD3605-RESPONS
                 FROM COVT3605_PROJECTS
                 WHERE NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND ICTACUST    = :COCD3605-ICTACUST
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT3605
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF DB2-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ1-S
              MOVE COCK0001-PROJ-NAO-EXIST
                TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ1-MSG
              MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                TO COCV6811-CIDPROJ1-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       2800-LER-PROJECTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * LER RESPONSAVEL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2850-LER-RESPONS.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT NTRABALHADOR
                  , GNOME
                  , CEMPRESA
                  , CUTILIZA
               INTO :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
                  , :COCD5303-GNOME
                  , :COCD5303-CEMPRESA
                  , :COCD5303-CUTILIZA
               FROM COVT5303_PESSOAS
            WHERE NTRABALHADOR = :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5303               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2850-LER-RESPONS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * LER NIVEIS DE APROVAﾇﾃO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2900-LER-NIVEIS.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT NIDPROJECTO
                      , CUSER01
                      , CUSER02
                 INTO  :COCD6600-NIDPROJECTO
                    ,  :COCD6600-CUSER01
                    ,  :COCD6600-CUSER02
                 FROM COVT6600
                 WHERE NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6600-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT6600
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2900-LER-NIVEIS-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2150-INSERE-DADOS1
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2150-INSERE-DADOS1.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-INSERE-DADOS1' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE CON-MANUAL
             TO COCD4804-CNUMFICH
           MOVE COCV6810-CFUNCIONARIO
             TO COCD4804-CIDEMP
           MOVE COCV6810-XDESCCFUNCIONARIO
             TO COCD4804-GNOMEEMP
           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I
             TO COCD4804-DTPROC

           MOVE COCV6810-CANO
             TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
           MOVE COCV6810-CMES
             TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
           MOVE CON-01
             TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO
             TO COCD4804-DTMESANO

           MOVE COCV6810-CIDDESP1
             TO COCD4804-CIDDESP
           MOVE COCV6810-XDESCCIDDESP1
             TO COCD4804-TIPODESPESA
           MOVE COCV6810-MVLR1
             TO COCD4804-MVLR
           MOVE COCV6810-DTREG1
             TO COCD4804-DTREG
           MOVE COCV6810-CMOED1
             TO COCD4804-CMOED

           MOVE WS-CLIENTE1
             TO COCD4804-CIDCLIENTE
           MOVE WS-GNOMECLI1
             TO COCD4804-GCLIENTE
           MOVE COCV6810-CIDPROJ1
             TO COCD4804-CIDPROJ
           MOVE WS-CPROJECT1
             TO COCD4804-GPROJ
           MOVE COCV6810-GOBSERV1
             TO COCD4804-GOBSERV
           MOVE COCV6810-GTRAJECTO1
             TO COCD4804-GTRAJECTO
           MOVE COCV6810-NKMS1
             TO COCD4804-NKMS
           MOVE COCV6810-GMOTIVO1
             TO COCD4804-GMOTIVO
           MOVE COCV6810-IPAYROLL1
             TO COCD4804-IPAYROLL
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I
             TO COCD4804-CUSERID
           MOVE SPACES
             TO COCD4804-HTIMEST

           MOVE WS-NSEQ1
             TO COCD4804-NSEQ

           MOVE CON-IN
             TO COCD4804-CSITU

      *--- Dados da Empresa
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6810-CEMPRESA NOT EQUAL SPACES
               PERFORM 2501-BUSCA-EMPRESA
                  THRU 2501-BUSCA-EMPRESA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD5403-GNOME
             TO COCD4804-GEMPRESA

      *--- Dados Pais
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               PERFORM 2503-BUSCA-PAIS
                  THRU 2503-BUSCA-PAIS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-GPAIS
             TO COCD4804-GPAIS

      *--- Dados Linha Negio
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               MOVE WS-LINHANEG1 TO WS-LINHANEG
               PERFORM 2504-BUSCA-LNEG
                  THRU 2504-BUSCA-LNEG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-LNEG
             TO COCD4804-GNEGOC

      **R  MOVE COCD5403-CMOEDA
      **R    TO COCD4804-CMOEDPAIS
           MOVE WS-CMOED-FUNC
             TO COCD4804-CMOEDPAIS
           MOVE COCV6810-CEMPRESA
             TO COCD4804-CEMPRESA
           MOVE COCD5403-CPAIS
             TO COCD4804-CPAIS
           MOVE WS-CUTILIZA1
             TO COCD4804-CUSER01
           MOVE WS-CUSER1-01
